{"tid":360923,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友聽日生日，鬧左交。","createTime":"2017-08-15T16:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T11:51:11.000Z","uid":90506,"like":3,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f52a21343601b78a54cf7afb32e2bc3003e45ec1","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"男朋友聽日生日，啱啱同佢全家去左食飯，覺得好難堪。<br />\n<br />\n其實係因為好小事有小小冷戰咁啦，但今日晏就都有好返小小講下工作既野，夜晚拎住份禮物同佢屋企人食飯，但佢基乎全程黑口黑臉，連佢媽都問佢做咩咁既口臉，我覺得好難堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為平日我地係笑笑口有傾有講。<br />\n<br />\n然後泊好車行返屋企，諗住上佢到拆下禮物咪幾開心，點知佢問我，你上黎呀？我話係呀一齊拆禮物，佢：「但我好眼訓，一陣返去就訓。」<br />\n<br />\n咁點呀，你全家人都係後面，姐係要我即刻轉身話返屋企？<br />\n個下差啲喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唯有厚臉皮話拆埋先訓啦。<br />\n<br />\n上到去佢冇理我，玩左陣手機就訓⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽朝點氹佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2b04823198966639c72663032ba4abbc543737","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"洗撚理佢"},{"pid":"6cf095298ab17272821a20877c4aeb7950e06e73","tid":360923,"uid":29276,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:44:59.000Z","msg":"你有無幫佢打飛機？"},{"pid":"c8ad60dbf128187ddce3f181d86039ecabede30a","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":100,"dislike":5,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"同佢講分手啦 唔撚識尊重人"},{"pid":"00f6442a56caa30048aa7ed68a21a15b0f8530c9","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 成家人係到都咁"},{"pid":"cea7abfb44f22dc3274e5da37d9c37a239f69172","tid":360923,"uid":20270,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"所謂好小事係乜？？"},{"pid":"7065d258180fa93ca647ed8adb56463f3a3daa95","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"下次得你地2個<br />\n隨時打埋你"},{"pid":"172843c1e6bd3614233da54b939bdcfd2e46da57","tid":360923,"uid":31693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:46:09.000Z","msg":"係咪發現左你啲秘密"},{"pid":"5a63c398ac4c28888bf337d8d671e131e125e0bb","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"我係你真係唔忍"},{"pid":"82e949a549d9386ee5d7cf7353083b654591fe6d","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"佢覺得生日大曬？"},{"pid":"4a0e0f7c11c00b22dfd211900635df9fae05ad54","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗撚理佢</blockquote><br />\n如果平日我應該會繼續嬲，不過佢生日，唔好啦"},{"pid":"2e3c27f55e4460d92e57fdb4c4dbefcabf448871","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"仲要tum番佢？咪屈服"},{"pid":"022acf0a6e41b95b7845d1478144dfa6b0ecfe2c","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"不過你上黎都係呻下姐"},{"pid":"bf99dd6a93c2f73d99b5a68a0fec80ac5330350c","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所謂好小事係乜？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚小事，不過太on9唔太想講<br />\n反正係啲溝通上既小錯誤，後來佢都認左錯<br />\n但個氣氛keep住尷尬"},{"pid":"76e63a9c5176b204afb104f53f4066dd45f5e431","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪發現左你啲秘密</blockquote><br />\n冇秘密，咩都比佢睇"},{"pid":"569d53f0922d5db6105dd1de946df6d924c3312f","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"睇死你都係死死氣tum佢"},{"pid":"47ef890fa8f74470068616679ec4bf01880ae8c6","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所謂好小事係乜？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚小事，不過太on9唔太想講<br />\n反正係啲溝通上既小錯誤，後來佢都認左錯<br />\n但個氣氛keep住尷尬</blockquote><br />\n佢認左錯仲黑9你面"},{"pid":"10e7bd406d77264091d647cf6445f262cccb6b86","tid":360923,"uid":1833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所謂好小事係乜？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚小事，不過太on9唔太想講<br />\n反正係啲溝通上既小錯誤，後來佢都認左錯<br />\n但個氣氛keep住尷尬</blockquote><br />\n肯定你係on9喇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講嚟聽下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf5ff246a7be950d7525634b32afc4243c880a2","tid":360923,"uid":127508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講分手啦 唔撚識尊重人</blockquote><br />\n完全認同。<br />\n好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd943f2f778a6f82f5d58d3a48150812f239db9","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過你上黎都係呻下姐</blockquote><br />\nYes，因為我都好小氣<br />\n自己谷住會唔開心，聽日佢生日唔想咁。<br />\n講出黎舒服啲聽日先有心機氹佢。"},{"pid":"72fd3e267c4a6476215a63e48c809a265c093507","tid":360923,"uid":69332,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"樓主，我只可以答你男人好快會無事<br />\n講句對唔住，咩都可以化解曬<br />\n男人其實好簡單"},{"pid":"4a23a13f0e2000c2290c0120a826cb076c1794ee","tid":360923,"uid":127508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過你上黎都係呻下姐</blockquote><br />\nYes，因為我都好小氣<br />\n自己谷住會唔開心，聽日佢生日唔想咁。<br />\n講出黎舒服啲聽日先有心機氹佢。</blockquote><br />\n平時佢會嬲幾耐？<br />\n如果聽日全日黑面你都照哄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09deae9a01dfe2687695ad371cb34e898a27e419","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同佢講分手啦 唔撚識尊重人</blockquote><br />\n完全認同。<br />\n好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小家到咁 你諗清楚嫁唔嫁比佢"},{"pid":"8fdc33f634b2ff0f563543fb2e89c37d97b660c7","tid":360923,"uid":130140,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"通常點鬧交都好，對住大家嘅屋企人都應該要扮下無野啦，佢喺佢屋企人面前咁對你，擺明唔比臉你，亦唔尊重你。你咁都諗住要氹返佢唔係叫大方，而係叫on撚9"},{"pid":"a3482fbb7d87495bc412c9046e02924bd74c497d","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所謂好小事係乜？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚小事，不過太on9唔太想講<br />\n反正係啲溝通上既小錯誤，後來佢都認左錯<br />\n但個氣氛keep住尷尬</blockquote><br />\n肯定你係on9喇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講嚟聽下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實應該係佢做野做到忟忟地，因為佢工作量好大，又準備創業好大壓力，我係佢做野時唔小心講錯小小野咁"},{"pid":"8a83bcc415e65fbf900234c4e31aadb00292af1b","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過你上黎都係呻下姐</blockquote><br />\nYes，因為我都好小氣<br />\n自己谷住會唔開心，聽日佢生日唔想咁。<br />\n講出黎舒服啲聽日先有心機氹佢。</blockquote><br />\n平時佢會嬲幾耐？<br />\n如果聽日全日黑面你都照哄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人老狗要嬲得咁耐"},{"pid":"aa14a0f4b190f0bef8eeab12dcfd9ee6d769940d","tid":360923,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"含啦"},{"pid":"c355c55cbc6f03aa8b146f789257aa53a8813e98","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主，我只可以答你男人好快會無事<br />\n講句對唔住，咩都可以化解曬<br />\n男人其實好簡單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經講過，今日晏就買左野飲去佢公司探下佢，諗住佢會開心小小，但佢都係唔多出聲又冇咩笑容，坐左陣就忍唔住走左。"},{"pid":"09feab638c01592eed18b05c4b7a2c5ec113be93","tid":360923,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所謂好小事係乜？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚小事，不過太on9唔太想講<br />\n反正係啲溝通上既小錯誤，後來佢都認左錯<br />\n但個氣氛keep住尷尬</blockquote><br />\n肯定你係on9喇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講嚟聽下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實應該係佢做野做到忟忟地，因為佢工作量好大，又準備創業好大壓力，我係佢做野時唔小心講錯小小野咁</blockquote><br />\n講錯乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869495cb32c8376f5d70ccd5a5770f39ed67e714","tid":360923,"uid":127508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同佢講分手啦 唔撚識尊重人</blockquote><br />\n完全認同。<br />\n好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小家到咁 你諗清楚嫁唔嫁比佢</blockquote><br />\n以前男朋友就係咁，<br />\n勁痴線，<br />\n講錯一句野（其實可能唔記得佢住嗰度叫咩名），<br />\n就黑我面全日，<br />\n我嗰時仲要傻下傻下咁哄佢，<br />\n最後頂唔順飛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7ab2c8764700b04fb65fd7b1b4bf29a14da602","tid":360923,"uid":127508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主，我只可以答你男人好快會無事<br />\n講句對唔住，咩都可以化解曬<br />\n男人其實好簡單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經講過，今日晏就買左野飲去佢公司探下佢，諗住佢會開心小小，但佢都係唔多出聲又冇咩笑容，坐左陣就忍唔住走左。</blockquote><br />\n樓主其實你盡咗力，你已經好好。"},{"pid":"926e4bbee6b69ec2d6086fe56bc8b7f9a3eac7b9","tid":360923,"uid":6783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主，我只可以答你男人好快會無事<br />\n講句對唔住，咩都可以化解曬<br />\n男人其實好簡單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經講過，今日晏就買左野飲去佢公司探下佢，諗住佢會開心小小，但佢都係唔多出聲又冇咩笑容，坐左陣就忍唔住走左。</blockquote><br />\n白痴 我係你就唔理番佢 大帝咩嫁下 下下要人哄 互相尊重都唔識"},{"pid":"d54b8c0e94f3b12f32660d2afd6216dc6881f27d","tid":360923,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"講多句，生日唔係大哂。<br />\n不過你聽日咪扮下無野先囉，當比個下台階大家。如果佢仲將今日嘅情緒帶埋落聽日，咁你真係要諗下佢有幾值得你r爛臉咁氹。"},{"pid":"9a536c2b73f0f939dad3d9a8796464acd224c9f4","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過你上黎都係呻下姐</blockquote><br />\nYes，因為我都好小氣<br />\n自己谷住會唔開心，聽日佢生日唔想咁。<br />\n講出黎舒服啲聽日先有心機氹佢。</blockquote><br />\n平時佢會嬲幾耐？<br />\n如果聽日全日黑面你都照哄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係一日半日咁啦。<br />\n氹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽日book左間聽聞好好既餐廳，希望佢開心啲啦。"},{"pid":"001fc39764a671ac034dd838dd08d027c3f51ddb","tid":360923,"uid":127508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過你上黎都係呻下姐</blockquote><br />\nYes，因為我都好小氣<br />\n自己谷住會唔開心，聽日佢生日唔想咁。<br />\n講出黎舒服啲聽日先有心機氹佢。</blockquote><br />\n平時佢會嬲幾耐？<br />\n如果聽日全日黑面你都照哄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係一日半日咁啦。<br />\n氹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽日book左間聽聞好好既餐廳，希望佢開心啲啦。</blockquote><br />\n你加油哄佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常情況下自己女朋友成晚認晒低威死晒狗咁都會下啖氣啦，<br />\n仲要係小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主平時點忍佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590268ac6e94471caa8db45056c37b034464fe1d","tid":360923,"uid":90506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同佢講分手啦 唔撚識尊重人</blockquote><br />\n完全認同。<br />\n好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小家到咁 你諗清楚嫁唔嫁比佢</blockquote><br />\n以前男朋友就係咁，<br />\n勁痴線，<br />\n講錯一句野（其實可能唔記得佢住嗰度叫咩名），<br />\n就黑我面全日，<br />\n我嗰時仲要傻下傻下咁哄佢，<br />\n最後頂唔順飛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最唔開心