女朋友成晚認晒低威死晒狗咁都會下啖氣啦，<br />\n仲要係小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主平時點忍佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔嬲時真係好好，溫柔體貼斯文有幽默感。<br />\n大部分時間都係用黎陪我。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實都係嗰句，一個願打一個願捱，<br />\n最緊要自己覺得開心幸福，<br />\n我就自問對住小氣男人開心唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3899dec5dda57a5e3e9bbb1740b9812c19f34f3","tid":360923,"uid":135900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"做男人做到咁小家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381fa91e59f28430b8e10402017be3f4049a057d","tid":360923,"uid":127508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同佢講分手啦 唔撚識尊重人</blockquote><br />\n完全認同。<br />\n好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小家到咁 你諗清楚嫁唔嫁比佢</blockquote><br />\n以前男朋友就係咁，<br />\n勁痴線，<br />\n講錯一句野（其實可能唔記得佢住嗰度叫咩名），<br />\n就黑我面全日，<br />\n我嗰時仲要傻下傻下咁哄佢，<br />\n最後頂唔順飛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最唔開心係有時主動撩下佢，但佢唔理我<br />\n即刻灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見住你就諗返起以前既我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同一個小氣既男人一齊真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n脫左苦海咪好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最弊佢小家到前嗰幾個月突登拖住女朋友喺我面前走嚟走去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肉鬼酸"},{"pid":"9f7d647cc25549f52768693bf50f328a08b3bd0c","tid":360923,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:02:02.000Z","msg":"好委屈"},{"pid":"d06e32a27165e680cfa08a4b3baf178cce43539d","tid":360923,"uid":75042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"應該無乜男人會因為一句野嬲咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n介唔介意成件事講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以句野令佢諗到第二啲野(E.g 踐踏佢夢想/努力，唔體諒佢唔了解佢etc)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316a234a7191e9a14a46ec5b5eda6bb95a16fac5","tid":360923,"uid":133042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"咁都忍得, 屎都食得啦... 分手吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對你一啲尊重都無"},{"pid":"f2efcbe22e0b1afabcf21ad14091223921cbe26d","tid":360923,"uid":70251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"女人小小事唔等於男人小小事喎<br />\n不如你大概講下咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac19dd599556e1ed942bbeb9b26917f0c78aa53","tid":360923,"uid":17232,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"咩小小事先，你啲女人有時明明自己錯又唔撚講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母覺得自己係受害者"},{"pid":"73aa7559af26d98177c9934afea035f560f6eb08","tid":360923,"uid":69332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主，我只可以答你男人好快會無事<br />\n講句對唔住，咩都可以化解曬<br />\n男人其實好簡單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經講過，今日晏就買左野飲去佢公司探下佢，諗住佢會開心小小，但佢都係唔多出聲又冇咩笑容，坐左陣就忍唔住走左。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放心啦，佢好快會無事<br />\n就好似我咁從來都唔忍心嬲佢，<br />\n因為對住自己愛既人好難會嬲得到佢"},{"pid":"4745ad3c7d3898c5c52e2e18929c17f442ca17f5","tid":360923,"uid":58066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"好多時你以爲小小事但佢根本唔係咁諗，想知你講左咩多d"},{"pid":"f62dc9f5a69762e92956689b1be037ff3658066a","tid":360923,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"抱下佢講句sorry就無事啦<br />\n好多時一個動作好過把口講一千句"},{"pid":"7a2ae3ee44fe5fee770827d9f95253726846e559","tid":360923,"uid":69332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔好睇到男人好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cb32551cd949491fe973edb80c414ab8ae5ef4","tid":360923,"uid":31306,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"點解你講錯野反而係佢道歉？<br />\n點解你一路都唔敢講講錯乜嘢只係話小小嘢？<br />\n有幾小？對你來講小定係對佢來講小？"},{"pid":"46ad15846a29be5ed481edc2ca7d12c1ab59e80f","tid":360923,"uid":20270,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你講錯野反而係佢道歉？<br />\n點解你一路都唔敢講講錯乜嘢只係話小小嘢？<br />\n有幾小？對你來講小定係對佢來講小？</blockquote><br />\n男朋友：唉 算喇 我錯喇屌"},{"pid":"a20c06d53b7015a1638cc257d224a76e8cd30df4","tid":360923,"uid":134636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"拿，你話好小野，當你啱，佢真係幾仆街，成日都係咁飛左佢，佢今日可以冷暴力你，第日佢真暴力你都似<br />\n但係如果唔係小野的話，咁佢可能真係好嬲，咁你就反省下啦"},{"pid":"3943bf5d2bc5a0807cb9cdeef3f222dbc7b585db","tid":360923,"uid":15389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"到呢刻樓主都唔肯講佢講錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323c41b45975992c2d55e0cd3242b49ee23afffe","tid":360923,"uid":70251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩小小事先，你啲女人有時明明自己錯又唔撚講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母覺得自己係受害者</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0f2895f410ba35ee272540fae20a452df792a2","tid":360923,"uid":41744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"擺到明樓主仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死都唔講咩事"},{"pid":"507a0b496d0a334496037f8aef52f6fe5519a2ad","tid":360923,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解你講錯野反而係佢道歉？<br />\n點解你一路都唔敢講講錯乜嘢只係話小小嘢？<br />\n有幾小？對你來講小定係對佢來講小？</blockquote><br />\n男朋友：唉 算喇 我錯喇屌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a9e9630aaa1388cda47c6a1ccade78813d9574","tid":360923,"uid":18417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"咁你男朋友一定係又靚仔又條件好大把女追， 我地呢D 條件差既男仔邊到夠彊發脾氣？ 永遠只有佢可以發我脾氣，永遠我氹佢冇佢氹我，真係你的樣子如何。"},{"pid":"5ca3b52cce2da8fb29aac6347867272cd7cc4d26","tid":360923,"uid":31306,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿，你話好小野，當你啱，佢真係幾仆街，成日都係咁飛左佢，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢今日可以冷暴力你，第日佢真暴力你都似</span><br />\n但係如果唔係小野的話，咁佢可能真係好嬲，咁你就反省下啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a46b70d48d743f9ec87b4125f969a989c35ac2","tid":360923,"uid":70251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拿，你話好小野，當你啱，佢真係幾仆街，成日都係咁飛左佢，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢今日可以冷暴力你，第日佢真暴力你都似</span><br />\n但係如果唔係小野的話，咁佢可能真係好嬲，咁你就反省下啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發脾氣就冷暴力<br />\n咁會唔會流曬血好痛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010168502286cb3afab927f036406c6fa4116766","tid":360923,"uid":47055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"你連你講錯咩都唔肯講，叫人點撐你？"},{"pid":"fa72e7de2f59d4c6a6c54c334363a1b72bf88c5d","tid":360923,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"分手要狠"},{"pid":"b1229e7e70a169ddbeb42518f71e253e17e8734a","tid":360923,"uid":80039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"其實個關鍵仲係好小事度 到依家都未肯講"},{"pid":"5a5e2754f2566ce0c2b8cf4ab850afd780beb2b3","tid":360923,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:31:17.000Z","msg":"聽埋本身佢嬲d乜先評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c801c6cdcb48ff950ba1d6a0b7f6c590edd4ff4","tid":360923,"uid":15220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>拿，你話好小野，當你啱，佢真係幾仆街，成日都係咁飛左佢，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢今日可以冷暴力你，第日佢真暴力你都似</span><br />\n但係如果唔係小野的話，咁佢可能真係好嬲，咁你就反省下啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發脾氣就冷暴力<br />\n咁會唔會流曬血好痛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑面都叫暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a3f3110a100c7cbd4de820470f586338890426","tid":360923,"uid":123578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友聽日生日，啱啱同佢全家去左食飯，覺得好難堪。<br />\n<br />\n其實係因為好小事有小小冷戰咁啦，但今日晏就都有好返小小講下工作既野，夜晚拎住份禮物同佢屋企人食飯，但佢基乎全程黑口黑臉，連佢媽都問佢做咩咁既口臉，我覺得好難堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為平日我地係笑笑口有傾有講。<br />\n<br />\n然後泊好車行返屋企，諗住上佢到拆下禮物咪幾開心，點知佢問我，你上黎呀？我話係呀一齊拆禮物，佢：「但我好眼訓，一陣返去就訓。」<br />\n<br />\n咁點呀，你全家人都係後面，姐係要我即刻轉身話返屋企？<br />\n個下差啲喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唯有厚臉皮話拆埋先訓啦。<br />\n<br />\n上到去佢冇理我，玩左陣手機就訓⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽朝點氹佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n攬住佢訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢就算訓訓下feel到都應該會攬返你。<br />\n可能佢真係太攰訓左姐！<br />\n我試過冷戰左成日，用呢招work!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8addce680a52c14cf16b5e97fd57fbf2b1f69772","tid":360923,"uid":59236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:08:06.000Z","msg":"屌 如果真係小小野<br />\n你講到佢平時咁好既男人點會嬲都咁<br />\n你話佢想創業 9成9 傷到佢自尊心<br />\n肯撚定你自己柒到裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384b4d9a651651fe8c1f481057158b62b1da58b5","tid":360923,"uid":88134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過你上黎都係呻下姐</blockquote><br />\nYes，因為我都好小氣<br />\n自己谷住會唔開心，聽日佢生日唔想咁。<br />\n講出黎舒服啲聽日先有心機氹佢。</blockquote><br />\n平時佢會嬲幾耐？<br />\n如果聽日全日黑面你都照哄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人老狗要嬲得咁耐</blockquote><br />\n有時因為唔嬲之後既日子就俾條女惡晒，食住晒，<br />\n所以佢咁其實都係可以理解既。"},{"pid":"0f29f5dfc53d96ce8428bef7dc191d693e36537c","tid":360923,"uid":69898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該無乜男人會因為一句野嬲咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n介唔介意成件事講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以句野令佢諗到第二啲野(E.g 踐踏佢夢想/努力，唔體諒佢唔了解佢etc)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得係咁<br />\n可能係無意中傷害左佢<br />\n但樓主仲以為係小事，當冇事<br />\n比着我會更嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efa7ce7ddeb3249c537d874203064f82fd07bb6","tid":360923,"uid":132223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽埋本身佢嬲d乜先評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇死樓主唔夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313103903f683a6a1b13326012c652cc7dfd5b2e","tid":360923,"uid":60518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:32:59.000Z","msg":"睇死樓主八婆笑鳩