ep住尷尬</blockquote><br />\n肯定你係on9喇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講嚟聽下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實應該係佢做野做到忟忟地，因為佢工作量好大，又準備創業好大壓力，我係佢做野時唔小心講錯小小野咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我覺得你地位危危地，good luck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地搞正經野就俾番空間人啦"},{"pid":"e83adfa1f4be68b79ccc6eb101d2dac6db35746f","tid":360923,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:37:27.000Z","msg":"你買咩禮物比佢"},{"pid":"ed85e92b9608f59f091a682315ebd1eed3e47077","tid":360923,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"個問題埋可能係你以為個句野小小事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc731693efc19ffbdc9f92aaaf06be902658a4e3","tid":360923,"uid":15389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"原來仲未講到底講錯啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 九成唔係小事而樓主驚講完畀連登仔屌到反艇，所以一路都係話講錯咗少少野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0336cf3f719604647d10954da52c1139ba024db5","tid":360923,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所謂好小事係乜？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚小事，不過太on9唔太想講<br />\n反正係啲溝通上既小錯誤，後來佢都認左錯<br />\n但個氣氛keep住尷尬</blockquote><br />\n證明佢係小氣鬼黎<br />\n邊個唔著都好<br />\n道完歉原諒左<br />\n就應該開開心心番嫁啦<br />\n做咩重要尷尷尬尬咁"},{"pid":"d249ce84a3f557e1640125b6c7f0607543e4046c","tid":360923,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過你上黎都係呻下姐</blockquote><br />\nYes，因為我都好小氣<br />\n自己谷住會唔開心，聽日佢生日唔想咁。<br />\n講出黎舒服啲聽日先有心機氹佢。</blockquote><br />\n平時佢會嬲幾耐？<br />\n如果聽日全日黑面你都照哄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人老狗要嬲得咁耐</blockquote><